      • NUM_THREADS_KEY

        public static final java.lang.String NUM_THREADS_KEY
        Key for integer property. Controls the number of threads employed by the interior-point optimizer. If set to a positive number MOSEK will use this number of threads. If set to zero, the number of threads used will equal the number of cores detected on the machine. Corresponds to the mosek.Env.iparam.intpnt_num_threads parameter.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • SOLVE_FORM_KEY

        public static final java.lang.String SOLVE_FORM_KEY
        Key for solveform property. Controls whether MOSEK will solve the problem as given ("primal"), swap the primal and dual ("dual", if supported), or be free to choose either ("free").
        See Also:
